g?1449719299\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2-mf-techbang.pixfs.net%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F32957%2Fmedium%2Fc64da7af0a75bf38b14b0ad1089b20b3.jpg%3F1449719299&h=78cc0784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第3名：後背肌<br />\n肌肉線條分明的後背寬度（記住，肩與臀圍的比例），佔了 79％ 的女人對男人的感知吸引力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2-mf-techbang.pixfs.net/system/images/32958/medium/e93fca2f414dea9d7c24de05253d67af.jpg?1449719301\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2-mf-techbang.pixfs.net%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F32958%2Fmedium%2Fe93fca2f414dea9d7c24de05253d67af.jpg%3F1449719301&h=ca1fa8b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第4名：手臂<br />\n強壯健碩的手臂是一個大轉折，是很多人的喜愛和青睞。大多的女人認為，那是男人將自己「身體照顧的很好」的有力證據，而且也承認喜歡從他們穿的短 T 或是針織衫來看一個男人的二頭肌，當然，強壯的手臂也意味著男人保護女人的能力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mf.techbang.com/posts/2111-juksy-men-sexy-site-survey-we-care-most-about-the-site-is-the-original\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmf.techbang.com%2Fposts%2F2111-juksy-men-sexy-site-survey-we-care-most-about-the-site-is-the-original&d=Zi3dU1milWSUjNvnFpVMMgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=dfe83f35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mf.techbang.com/posts/2111-juksy-men-sexy-site-survey-we-care-most-about-the-site-is-the-original</a>"},{"pid":"465073b2cc2934d99dd0cf211f9926600d3158d2","tid":588174,"uid":27793,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:45:48.000Z","msg":"男人身高＝女人樣貌 （超重要）<br />\n男人太瘦＝女人AA Cup（女人無胸令男人無性慾；男人太瘦＝女人咁，女人見到都無性慾）"},{"pid":"81639cc2d0c60da9e1b0068ebf5cfa4e80513447","tid":588174,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"279007f2b254de9eb572a01bb390cc4ae844f3f5","tid":588174,"uid":140590,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:45:39.000Z","msg":"男朋友大脾幼過我。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06:46:53.000Z","msg":"我都係..."},{"pid":"47a87eaf1fa105851146d30461391edefe14dd19","tid":588174,"uid":88001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T06